ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"媒體收錢收禮物要求好嚴謹，以下係2013年嘅有關報道：<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://hkthejournalist.blogspot.com/2010/04/blog-post_2759.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkthejournalist.blogspot.com%2F2010%2F04%2Fblog-post_2759.html&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL%2B9tl09raJ%2B2zMWOssuGUT0%3D&h=e6e9f5c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkthejournalist.blogspot.com/2010/04/blog-post_2759.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcp4cQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmcp4cQ4.jpg&h=3f27f391&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，去一個記者IG問過可唔可以請港聞記者、主播、攝影、工程食一餐下午茶，或者送少少物資（例如小食飲品），結果冇回覆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（講講下諗起撐警集會都係送嘢飲嘢食比警察。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n其實真係要正視返記者薪金問題，真係嚴重underpaid，良心媒體幫得就幫。<br />\n<br />\n利申：網上行用戶有埋now機頂盒，兩個月前我課金睇有線，屋企兩人有課蘋果。"},{"pid":"8656b0594a101ed67e6195b106474a64e0cf3b64","tid":1378348,"uid":269563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:20:47.000Z","msg":"都係齊思廣益<br />\n唯有再睇下有咩方法回饋記者"},{"pid":"45c47f89c5c85abf33a3f58500988e3b14045478","tid":1378348,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"發覺最近好多post又話要請食飯又話出bonus<br />\n<br />\n都係離唔開一個錢字同埋係p牌出post"},{"pid":"252b1e15c1ad1015efc6f3ec44f72efd65213077","tid":1378348,"uid":5502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"其他唔知，香港電台係政府既，唔收得"},{"pid":"a62afc77025771dcfae52164593d029ff29e3a3c","tid":1378348,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bbb07bdf6b323b21b348607c14d0f05e61dbcf1","tid":1378348,"uid":176657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:40:45.000Z","msg":"佢地呢兩個月真係返到好似戰地記者咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要比狗打 又食蛋 又中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢地公司對佢地好d 籌錢唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca45bafb22bfdf33b7547680ef00c1643ab2f21d","tid":1378348,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:42:13.000Z","msg":"等贏左場運動再要求(之後果個)政府改善下記者/媒體待遇好過啦<br />\n呢場仗贏唔撚到就大家冚球鏟到時身為大眾眼睛嘅第四權自然都會死於非命"},{"pid":"223f88175525f52c8be5b9db5c63e9dca21fcc1d","tid":1378348,"uid":293605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"前線記者真係好辛苦，食催淚彈，俾強光照，俾黑警打，搵命搏，仲要寫稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人工竟然低過班黑警一大截<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝所有前線記者（cctvb除外）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}